channel.title: Uhhh, help a noob out please
channel.description: umm, i hate to be a noob...... :o........ but looks like i am. what i need is a break of what a deob is and how the hell i'm supposed to use it. and moparscape...it's cool you get a 126 character but wtf...you can't get back to it. and there's not much to do with it. so yeah, help anyone?

item.title: Uhhh, help a noob out please
item.dc:creator: @RLN RLN
item.description:
@RLN wrote:

Jagex obfuscates(google it) their code so its hard to read and wont recompile without refactoring it. So someone had to write a deober, so we can edit/analyze the code in raw java instead of bytecode. Saev wrote the first one then other people enhanced it/implemented it in autodeobers, etc.
